t we derive for the\namplitude of the kick imparted on the companion neutron star at its birth\nindicates that the kick has been of low amplitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Nov 2006 16:04:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
