aring\nemission from Sgr A* at NIR and MIR wavelengths will enable us to distinguish\nbetween different kinds of flare models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Nov 2006 09:05:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
